etcher@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fletcher">弗莱彻 (FLETCHER)</a>宣布推出她的大二全长专辑《In Search Of The Antidote》，并发行了主打单曲《Lead Me On》。</p><ul><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fletcher-nme-affirmations-girl-of-my-dreams-3457242"><b>弗莱彻：“在我上台之前，我告诉自己：‘你就是那个婊子’”</b></a></li></ul><p>这位新泽西歌手的失恋歌曲于上周晚些时候发布，标志着她与 2022 年首张专辑《Girl Of My Dreams》中精致、梦幻的音景有所不同，转而偏向流行摇滚。弗莱彻（Fletcher）的“带领我登上我”，反思了一种单相思，它的诗句详细介绍了她和一个情人之间的差异（“<em>我是为了找到你 /，但是你的内心一直在奔跑 /从来没有朝我奔跑</em>”），然后才达到高潮一个宣泄的钩子：“<em>所以你为什么不带我去 /导致某些东西总比没有好</em>”。</p><p>曲目伴随着亚历山大·摩尔斯（Alexandre Moors）导演的视频，该视频描绘了这位歌手在波西米亚人占领的一栋大房子的房间里徘徊。观看下面的视频“带领我”： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="FLETCHER - 带领我前进（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/4paMNQf1b2o?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “带领我”是弗莱彻（Fletcher）即将发行的大二专辑“搜索解毒剂”的主打单曲，该专辑将于3月22日通过Capitol/EMI唱片发行 - <a href="https://shop.findingfletcher.com/?utm_source=Original&amp;utm_campaign=20240123&amp;utm_medium=channel.utm_medium&amp;utm_referrer=https%3A%2F%2Ffletcher.lnk.to%2FAntidotePR&amp;utm_board=capitol-records-us&amp;utm_country=US&amp;utm_linkurl=fletcher.lnk.to%2FAntidoteStore&amp;lf=2905bd0618392b8bf38960726dc0a8cc" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订您的副本。</p><p>詹妮弗·德维奥（Jennifer Decilveo）为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/take-that">《 That That That</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/miley-cyrus">Miley Cyrus</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hozier">Hozier</a> 》（That That That That）的行为写了曲目，他通过乔恩·<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jon-bellion">贝利恩（Jon Bellion）</a> ，朱莉娅·迈克尔斯（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/julia-michaels">Julia Michaels）</a> ，迈克尔·波拉克（Michael Pollack）等的歌曲创作贡献创造了唱片。</p><p>这位歌手在新闻稿中表示，该唱片将为粉丝提供“身份，不安全感，自我和自我实现”主题的内省性观察，得出的结论是“爱是解毒剂”。她写道：“多年来，我一直在许多事情中寻找解毒剂：女人，道路，舞台，粉丝，灵性和自我反思。” “制作这张专辑是一场发掘，深深地潜水，我问自己会真正治愈我，而我的最终意识到，爱是解毒剂。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C2fZqiPxHEr/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.37